---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="薬剤師派遣で時給3000円・16時退社｜家庭も収入も諦めない働き方"
  description="残業なしでしっかり稼ぐ。「家庭」も「収入」も「安心」も全部どりできる、薬剤師派遣という新しい働き方をご提案します。時給3,000円以上、16時退社OKの求人を厳選紹介。"
  bodyClass="pb-24 md:pb-0"
>
  <header
    class="bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-md shadow-sm absolute md:fixed w-full z-50 top-0 left-0 h-14 md:h-16 flex items-center justify-between px-4 md:px-8 border-b border-gray-100 transition-all duration-300"
  >
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 md:gap-4">
      <div class="inline-block select-none">
        <a href="/" class="block hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity">
          <img
            src="/assets/images/yakusupo_logo.svg"
            alt="薬剤師Support.com"
            class="h-6 md:h-8 w-auto"
          />
        </a>
      </div>

      <div
        class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 text-[10px] md:text-xs font-medium px-2 py-0.5 rounded flex items-center whitespace-nowrap"
      >
        <i class="fas fa-bell text-gray-400 mr-1.5 text-[10px]"></i>
        <span id="header-date-text">2025年12月更新</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <a
      href="#register"
      class="hidden md:inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-accent hover:bg-accent-hover text-white font-bold py-2 px-6 rounded-full transition shadow-md text-sm shiny-btn"
    >
      <i class="fas fa-search"></i> 求人を見る（無料）
    </a>
  </header>

  <section
    class="pt-14 md:pt-16 pb-8 md:pb-16 bg-gradient-to-b from-teal-50 via-white to-white relative overflow-hidden"
  >
    <div class="relative z-20">
      <div class="bg-gray-50 py-0.5 border-b border-gray-100">
        <div
          class="flex justify-center items-center gap-2 text-[10px] text-gray-400"
        >
          <span
            class="border border-gray-300 px-1 rounded-[2px] bg-white text-gray-400 font-medium scale-90"
            >PR</span
          >
          <span>本ページはプロモーションが含まれています</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div
      class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center relative z-10 animate-on-scroll opacity-0 translate-y-8 transition-all duration-1000 ease-out"
    >
      <div class="-mx-4 md:mx-0 relative mb-5 overflow-hidden shadow-soft">
        <a href="#register">
          <picture>
            <source
              media="(min-width: 768px)"
              srcset="/assets/images/main.webp"
              type="image/webp"
            />
            <source
              media="(min-width: 768px)"
              srcset="/assets/images/main.png"
            />

            <source srcset="/assets/images/main_sp.webp" type="image/webp" />

            <img
              src="/assets/images/main_sp.png"
              alt="派遣にして笑顔で働く女性薬剤師"
              class="w-full h-auto align-middle object-cover"
              width="375"
              height="500"
              fetchpriority="high"
              decoding="async"
            />
          </picture>
        </a>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-gray-600 mt-6 mb-0 md:mb-8 leading-snug">
        <span class="font-bold">単発・スポットで時給3,000円！</span><br
          class="md:hidden"
        />
        扶養内で賢く稼ぎたい薬剤師の正解は
        <span class="text-accent font-bold decoration-accent/30 decoration-4"
          >“派遣”</span
        >でした
      </h1>

      <div class="hidden md:inline-flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
        <span class="text-accent font-bold text-sm animate-bounce">
          ＼ 最短60秒で入力完了！ ／
        </span>
        <a
          href="#register"
          class="hidden md:inline-flex shiny-btn group items-center justify-center w-full md:w-auto min-w-[340px] bg-accent hover:bg-accent-hover text-white text-xl font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-full shadow-lg shadow-accent/30 transition transform hover:-translate-y-1"
        >
          無料で求人紹介を受ける
          <i
            class="fas fa-chevron-right ml-3 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition"
          ></i>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="w-full">
    <section class="w-full bg-slate-50 pt-16 md:pt-24 pb-24 md:pb-32 relative">
      <div
        class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 relative z-10 animate-on-scroll opacity-0 translate-y-8 transition-all duration-1000 ease-out"
      >
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2
            class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold leading-tight text-slate-800"
          >
            今の職場、こんな<span class="text-accent relative inline-block"
              >悩み</span
            ><br class="md:hidden" />ありませんか？
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-10 md:gap-10">
          <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 relative">
            <div
              class="absolute -left-4 -bottom-4 w-full h-full bg-slate-200 rounded-[2rem] -z-10 hidden md:block transform -rotate-2"
            >
            </div>
            <div class="relative transform -rotate-2">
              <img
                src="/assets/images/full.png"
                alt="焦る薬剤師"
                class="w-full aspect-[4/3] object-cover rounded-[2rem] shadow-xl shadow-slate-300/50 grayscale-[30%]"
                loading="lazy"
              />
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-slate-900/10 rounded-[2rem]">
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
            <h3
              class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-slate-700 mb-10 text-center md:text-left"
            >
              正社員・パートの現実…
            </h3>

            <ul class="space-y-10">
              <li class="flex items-start group">
                <div class="shrink-0 mr-3">
                  <div class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-thermometer text-accent text-3xl"></i>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4
                    class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2 leading-tight"
                  >
                    子どもの発熱で早退のたびに肩身が狭い…
                  </h4>
                  <p
                    class="text-slate-500 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed"
                  >
                    「また？」という空気感。謝ってばかりで心がすり減っていく。
                  </p>
                </div>
              </li>

              <li class="flex items-start group">
                <div class="shrink-0 mr-3">
                  <div class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <i class="fas fa-business-time text-accent text-3xl"></i>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4
                    class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2 leading-tight"
                  >
                    「残業できません」が言いづらい空気
                  </h4>
                  <p
                    class="text-slate-500 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed"
                  >
                    定時で帰るのが悪のような雰囲気。周りに合わせて無理をしてしまう。
                  </p>
                </div>
              </li>

              <li class="flex items-start group">
                <div class="shrink-0 mr-3">
                  <div class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <i class="fas fa-user-slash text-accent text-3xl"></i>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4
                    class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2 leading-tight"
                  >
                    社員だと休めない。パートは収入が不安…
                  </h4>
                  <p
                    class="text-slate-500 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed"
                  >
                    責任と自由、どちらを選んでも何かが犠牲になるジレンマ。
                  </p>
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="absolute left-0 right-0 bottom-0 flex justify-center translate-y-[99%] z-20"
      >
        <div
          class="w-0 h-0 border-l-[40px] border-l-transparent border-r-[40px] border-r-transparent border-t-[30px] border-t-slate-50"
        >
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="w-full bg-white pt-24 md:pt-32 pb-16 md:pb-24 relative z-0">
      <div
        class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 animate-on-scroll opacity-0 translate-y-8 transition-all duration-1000 ease-out"
      >
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2
            class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 leading-tight"
          >
            <span class="text-teal-600">“派遣”</span>という新しい選択肢
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div
          class="flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-10 md:gap-10"
        >
          <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 relative">
            <div
              class="absolute -right-4 -bottom-4 w-full h-full bg-yellow-100 rounded-[2rem] -z-10 hidden md:block transform rotate-2"
            >
            </div>
            <div class="relative transform rotate-2">
              <img
                src="/assets/images/after-haken.png"
                alt="笑顔の親子"
                class="w-full aspect-[4/3] object-cover rounded-[2rem] shadow-2xl shadow-yellow-100/50"
                loading="lazy"
              />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
            <ul class="space-y-10">
              <li class="flex items-start group">
                <div class="shrink-0 mr-3">
                  <div class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <i class="fas fa-calendar-check text-teal-600 text-3xl"></i>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">
                    <span
                      class="bg-gradient-to-t from-yellow-200/60 to-transparent bg-[length:100%_40%] bg-bottom bg-no-repeat pb-1"
                      >週2日〜OK</span
                    >、家庭優先
                  </h4>
                  <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">
                    土日休みや時短勤務も自由自在。家族との時間を犠牲にしません。
                  </p>
                </div>
              </li>

              <li class="flex items-start group">
                <div class="shrink-0 mr-3">
                  <div class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <i class="fas fa-clock text-teal-600 text-3xl"></i>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                    <h4 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800">
                      定時退社！残業なし
                    </h4>
                  </div>
                  <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">
                    契約通りの時間で終了。「周りの目が気になって帰れない」から解放されます。
                  </p>
                </div>
              </li>

              <li class="flex items-start group">
                <div class="shrink-0 mr-3">
                  <div class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-piggy-bank text-teal-600 text-3xl"
                    ></i>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">
                    時給<span
                      class="text-teal-600 text-2xl md:text-3xl font-extrabold mx-1"
                      >3,000</span
                    >円〜も可能
                  </h4>
                  <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">
                    パートよりも高時給。短い時間でも、しっかりと家計を支えられます。
                  </p>
                </div>
              </li>

              <li class="flex items-start group">
                <div class="shrink-0 mr-3">
                  <div class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <i class="fas fa-shield-heart text-teal-600 text-3xl"></i>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">
                    福利厚生・ブランク研修
                  </h4>
                  <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">
                    <span class="font-bold text-teal-600">社会保険・有給</span
                    >も完備。復職支援プログラムがあるから久しぶりでも安心。
                  </p>
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 px-4 bg-teal-50/50 border-teal-100">
    <div
      class="max-w-6xl mx-auto animate-on-scroll opacity-0 translate-y-8 transition-all duration-1000 ease-out"
    >
      <h2 class="text-center text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-8 md:mb-16">
        「働き方を変えてよかった」<br />先輩ママの声
      </h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div
          class="bg-white p-6 pt-10 md:p-8 md:pt-12 rounded-2xl shadow-soft relative mt-6 md:mt-0 border border-gray-100"
        >
          <div
            class="absolute -top-6 md:-top-8 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2"
          >
            <img
              src="/assets/images/user01.png"
              alt="User"
              loading="lazy"
              class="w-16 h-16 md:w-20 md:h-20 rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-md object-cover"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <span
              class="inline-block bg-gray-100 text-gray-500 text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded mb-3"
              >34歳・子供2人</span
            >
            <span
              class="inline-block bg-gray-100 text-teal-600 text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded mb-3"
              >高時給派遣・エリア重視</span
            >
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-lg mb-5 leading-snug">
              お迎えの焦りから解放。<br />
              通勤時間が<span class="text-accent">30分短縮!</span>
            </h3>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 mb-4 text-sm">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
                <span class="text-gray-400 text-xs">転職前</span>
                <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium line-through"
                  >通勤45分・残業あり</span
                >
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                <span class="text-teal-600 text-xs font-bold">現在</span>
                <span class="text-gray-800 font-bold text-base"
                  >通勤15分・残業ゼロ</span
                >
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-sub-text text-left leading-relaxed">
              以前は延長保育に頼り切りでしたが、今は16時に退社。自宅近くのクリニックを紹介してもらい、夕飯を子供と作る余裕が生まれました。
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div id="more-reviews" class="hidden md:contents">
          <div
            class="bg-white p-6 pt-10 md:p-8 md:pt-12 rounded-2xl shadow-soft relative mt-10 md:mt-0 border border-gray-100 animate-fade-in"
          >
            <div
              class="absolute -top-6 md:-top-8 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2"
            >
              <img
                src="/assets/images/user02.png"
                alt="User"
                loading="lazy"
                class="w-16 h-16 md:w-20 md:h-20 rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-md object-cover"
                loading="lazy"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <span
                class="inline-block bg-gray-100 text-gray-500 text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded mb-3"
                >42歳・扶養内希望</span
              >
              <span
                class="inline-block bg-gray-100 text-teal-600 text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded mb-3"
                >高時給派遣</span
              >
              <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-lg mb-5 leading-snug">
                働く時間は減ったのに、<br />
                時給<span class="text-accent">900円UP</span>で収入維持！
              </h3>
              <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 mb-4 text-sm">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
                  <span class="text-gray-400 text-xs">転職前</span>
                  <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium line-through"
                    >時給 2,200円</span
                  >
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                  <span class="text-teal-600 text-xs font-bold">現在</span>
                  <span class="text-gray-800 font-bold text-base"
                    >時給 3,100円</span
                  >
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-sub-text text-left leading-relaxed">
                「派遣はハードルが高い」と思っていましたが、担当者の交渉で扶養内調整もスムーズに。短時間で効率よく家計を支えられています。
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div
            class="bg-white p-6 pt-10 md:p-8 md:pt-12 rounded-2xl shadow-soft relative mt-10 md:mt-0 border border-gray-100 animate-fade-in"
          >
            <div
              class="absolute -top-6 md:-top-8 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2"
            >
              <img
                src="/assets/images/user03.png"
                alt="User"
                loading="lazy"
                class="w-16 h-16 md:w-20 md:h-20 rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-md object-cover"
                loading="lazy"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <span
                class="inline-block bg-gray-100 text-gray-500 text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded mb-3"
                >39歳・ブランク3年</span
              >
              <span
                class="inline-block bg-gray-100 text-teal-600 text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded mb-3"
                >リハビリ復帰</span
              >
              <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-lg mb-5 leading-snug">
                新薬知識ゼロから復帰。<br />
                <span class="text-accent">週3日・1日4時間</span>で再スタート
              </h3>
              <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 mb-4 text-sm">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
                  <span class="text-gray-400 text-xs">不安</span>
                  <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium line-through"
                    >知識不足・体力</span
                  >
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                  <span class="text-teal-600 text-xs font-bold">現在</span>
                  <span class="text-gray-800 font-bold text-base"
                    >研修充実・監査メイン</span
                  >
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-sub-text text-left leading-relaxed">
                いきなりのフルタイムは怖かったので、理解のある店舗を紹介してもらいました。e-learningでの研修制度も使えて、自信を取り戻せました。
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 text-center md:hidden">
        <button
          id="show-more-btn"
          onclick="toggleReviews()"
          class="bg-white border border-gray-300 text-gray-600 font-bold py-3 px-10 rounded-full shadow-sm hover:bg-gray-50 transition active:scale-95 text-sm flex items-center mx-auto gap-2"
        >
          <span>他の口コミも見る</span>
          <i class="fas fa-chevron-down text-xs"></i>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <script is:inline>
    function toggleReviews() {
      const moreReviews = document.getElementById("more-reviews");
      const btn = document.getElementById("show-more-btn");
      moreReviews.classList.remove("hidden");
      btn.style.display = "none";
    }
  </script>

  <section class="bg-gray-100 py-16 md:py-24 px-4 overflow-hidden">
    <div
      class="max-w-7xl mx-auto animate-on-scroll opacity-0 translate-y-8 transition-all duration-1000 ease-out"
    >
      <h2 class="text-center text-2xl font-bold mb-3">
        例えば、こんな求人があります
      </h2>
      <p class="text-center text-xs text-sub-text mb-8 md:mb-12">
        ※実際の内容は派遣求人先でご確認ください
      </p>

      <div class="swiper mySwiper px-4">
        <div class="swiper-wrapper !items-stretch">
          <div class="swiper-slide !h-auto !flex">
            <div
              class="w-full bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-md border-t-4 border-primary relative flex flex-col overflow-hidden h-full"
            >
              <div class="h-32 bg-gray-200 w-full relative shrink-0">
                <img
                  src="/assets/images/ex01.png"
                  alt="職場の雰囲気"
                  class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                  loading="lazy"
                />
                <span
                  class="absolute top-3 right-3 bg-accent text-white text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded-full shadow-sm"
                  >週2日でも可能</span
                >
              </div>
              <div class="p-6 flex flex-col flex-grow">
                <div
                  class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-3 text-[10px] font-bold text-sub-text"
                >
                  <span class="bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded">調剤薬局</span>
                  <span class="bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded"
                    >土日休み相談可</span
                  >
                  <span class="bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded">16時退社</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-base text-gray-800 mb-4 leading-snug">
                  ママさん薬剤師活躍中！急なお休みも協力体制あり
                </h3>
                <div
                  class="flex flex-col gap-2 mt-auto pt-4 border-t border-gray-100"
                >
                  <div class="flex items-center text-sm">
                    <span class="w-12 font-bold text-gray-400 text-xs"
                      >時給</span
                    ><span class="font-bold text-accent text-lg">3,300円</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex items-center text-sm">
                    <span class="w-12 font-bold text-gray-400 text-xs"
                      >時間</span
                    ><span class="font-bold text-gray-700">9:00〜15:00</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="swiper-slide !h-auto !flex">
            <div
              class="w-full bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-md border-t-4 border-primary relative flex flex-col overflow-hidden h-full"
            >
              <div class="h-32 bg-gray-200 w-full shrink-0">
